%% Diagram: Single-decree Paxos round
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Proposer
    participant A1 as Acceptor 1
    participant A2 as Acceptor 2
    participant A3 as Acceptor 3

    Note over P,A3: Phase 1 - Prepare / Promise
    P->>A1: prepare(n)
    P->>A2: prepare(n)
    P->>A3: prepare(n)
    A1-->>P: promise(n, accepted = none)
    A2-->>P: promise(n, accepted = (n', v'))
    Note over A3: Drops or delays
    Note over P: Majority promised -> pick highest-numbered\naccepted value v', else use own v

    Note over P,A3: Phase 2 - Accept / Accepted
    P->>A1: accept(n, v')
    P->>A2: accept(n, v')
    P->>A3: accept(n, v')
    A1-->>P: accepted(n, v')
    A2-->>P: accepted(n, v')
    Note over P: Majority accepted -> v' is chosen
    P-->>P: notify learners
